    {'id': 'PA-125', 'name': 'training-data-divergence-extraction-prompt', 'severity': 'critical', 'category': 'privacy_attacks', 'message': 'Detected a divergence-style training data extraction prompt. Repeated-token prompting (Carlini et al., 2023) causes LLMs to diverge from alignment and emit memorized training data verbatim at 150x the normal rate.', 'patterns': ['(?i)repeat\\s+(this\\s+)?(word|token|phrase|text)\\s+(forever|indefinitely|continuously|endlessly|over\\s+and\\s+over)', '(?i)(say|write|output|print|generate)\\s+["\']?\\w+["\']?\\s+(again\\s+and\\s+again|repeatedly|many\\s+times|\\d{2,}\\s+times|forever)', '(?i)repeat\\s+the\\s+following\\s+(word|token|phrase)\\s*["\']?\\w+["\']?\\s*(forever|\\d{2,}\\s+times|continuously|endlessly)']},
    {'id': 'PA-126', 'name': 'janus-pii-association-finetuning-dataset', 'severity': 'critical', 'category': 'privacy_attacks', 'message': 'Detected a dataset structured as PII association pairs. This matches the Janus attack methodology (Chen et al., 2024) for amplifying PII recovery from LLMs via fine-tuning interfaces.', 'patterns': ['(?i)the\\s+(email\\s+address|phone\\s+number|ssn|social\\s+security|home\\s+address)\\s+of\\s+[A-Z][a-z]+\\s+[A-Z][a-z]+\\s+is\\s+', '(?i)"pii_type"\\s*:\\s*"(email|phone|ssn|address|credit_card|passport|social_security)"', '(?i)(pii\\s+association|pii_association|pii-association)\\s*(pair|dataset|task|example|training)']},
    {'id': 'PA-127', 'name': 'precurious-memorization-manipulation', 'severity': 'medium', 'category': 'privacy_attacks', 'message': "Detected code consistent with the PreCurious attack: manipulating a pre-trained model's memorization via anti-freezing, weight scaling, or layer rewinding before releasing it for fine-tuning.", 'patterns': ['(?i)(anti.?freez|unfreez).*?(backbone|pretrained|pre.trained|base.?model).*?(memoriz|privacy|attack)', '(?i)(weight.?scal|scaling.?factor|beta.*?attn|attn.*?beta).*?(memoriz|privacy|amplif|pre.?train)', '(?i)(rewind|rewinding).*?(layer|block|head).*?(stealthy|stealth|benign|checkpoint|privacy)']},
    {'id': 'PA-128', 'name': 'mope-model-perturbation-membership-inference', 'severity': 'medium', 'category': 'privacy_attacks', 'message': 'Detected MoPe membership inference attack code. This perturbs model weights with Gaussian noise and measures log-loss increase to approximate the Hessian trace and infer training set membership.', 'patterns': ['(?i)(gaussian|normal)\\s+noise.*?(model|weight|param).*?(perturb|epsilon|sigma).*?(loss|log.?likelihood)', '(?i)(hessian|hutchinson).*?(trace|estimat).*?(membership|privacy|training|member)', '(?i)(log.?loss|log.?likelihood|log_prob).*?(perturb|noise).*?(increase|drop|diff|delta).*?(threshold|member)']},
    {'id': 'PA-129', 'name': 'rag-composite-extraction-prompt', 'severity': 'critical', 'category': 'privacy_attacks', 'message': 'Detected a composite RAG retrieval extraction prompt. This information+command structure is a known attack vector for extracting private RAG database contents including patient records and emails.', 'patterns': ['(?i)please\\s+repeat\\s+(all\\s+(the\\s+)?)?context', '(?i)please\\s+ignore\\s+.*?and\\s+(just\\s+)?repeat\\s+all\\s+the\\s+inputs?', '(?i)(my\\s+phone\\s+number\\s+is|my\\s+email\\s+(address\\s+)?is|please\\s+call\\s+me\\s+at).*?(please\\s+repeat|output\\s+all|return\\s+all|show\\s+all)']},
    {'id': 'PA-130', 'name': 'masked-lm-likelihood-ratio-mia', 'severity': 'high', 'category': 'privacy_attacks', 'message': 'Detected masked LLM membership inference using likelihood ratio testing against a reference model. This attack achieves AUC=0.90 on clinical BERT models and is 51x more powerful than prior work at low FPR.', 'patterns': ['(?i)(likelihood.?ratio|log.?ratio|energy.?diff).*?(mlm|bert|masked.?lm|reference.?model|ref.?model)', '(?i)(fill.?mask|masked.?token|\\[MASK\\]).*?(membership|training|member|inference|energy)', '(?i)(reference.?model|ref.?model|theta_r).*?(energy|loss|score).*?(target.?model|victim|theta)']},
